about:
My aim is to provide the highest quality product possible. Quality is guaranteed because I am the one that grows it! If I wouldn't smoke it, I won't sell it! I operate on the 3S principles - the SAFETY, SECURITY and SATISFACTION of my customers is top priority :) Have been around for a bit, started on AB and Dream, CGMC and now happily Cannazon.

THE WEED
I only sell what I grow. All product is grown indoors and using exclusively organic nutrients. Harvested at the optimal time based on looking at the trichomes under the microscope. A few more details:

Grow Medium- soil or Coco Coir (indoor)
Nutrients- Exclusively liquid organic nutrients
Drying and curing- Conducted in controlled conditions, complete darkness with a temperature of +/- 20C and a 65% relative humidity for the initial slow dry and 60% RH for curing. That is the secret folks if you ever want to grow your own!

SHIPPING INFORMATION
We send anywhere in the EU. Other cases will be considered on an individual basis. Obviously no shipping to the USA as per Cannazon rules. 

Shipping is normally same day for orders received until noon. After that, order will go out latest next working day.  Orders that are marked as shipped HAVE been shipped, I never mark shipped without it being on the way. For opsec and logistical reasons, after packages have been dropped off it may take a few hours to mark them as shipped. 

Packages are prepared using proper stealth.

Delivery times:
Domestic orders - Next day delivery, unless the CTT screws things up :)
Western/Central EU - Normally 2-3 days, can take up to 5 days
Eastern EU - Normally 3-4 days, can take up to 5 days

There are always exceptions to the rules, especially during the holiday periods orders may take a little longer than usual. Please don't panic and let me know if your order has not arrived after 5 working days. 

PLEASE format your shipping details correctly to minimize the possiblity of lost packages or no-shows!

-----------------------------------------

Thanks for your interest and I appreciate your business. If you have a chance to leave feedback it is much appreciated! Let me know what you like or what you think I can do better. Any questions feel free to message me and I will respond as promptly as possible.
                

---------------


                    The Golden rule. I treat others like I like to be treated, hopefully you do the same!

No-shows: In the unusual event of a shipment that does not arrive, a reship or refund will be offered. My customers always get their stuff! But please remember the golden rule as karma is a bitch and of course this may affect your ability to order from me in the future.

Orders are shipped on working days only. Orders placed on Friday after 12PM, weekends and holidays will be shipped on the next working day. I prefer that orders don't sit for days in a box somewhere while the post office is closed.

POSTAGE/SHIPPING


We will get your order out for you the same day as you order SO LONG AS you have fulfilled all payment requirements and there is no issue with Name Address Format or any other problem that would prevent dispatch and so long as your order is received before 2pm (to allow us to pack and post). WE DON T SHIP ON SATURDAY OR SUNDAY.  As we are proud of our excellent reputation we are as keen for you to receive your product promptly as you are.

We will send you all necessary details in encrypted format to ensure you are kept up-to-date with deliveries.

 For all products:

We cannot however guarantee or confirm delivery and for this reason prior to postage we will require you to accept these two facts and accept that we hold no liability in this area.

Be ordering from us you are stating that you are aware that your parcel will have no tracking and that we are not responsible for ensuring delivery. Please don t use FAKE NAME. If the product is seized by customs we may offer a 25% reship. If you have any trouble with your order please CONTACT US before leaving a rating or review we will do everything we can to resolve the issue.

In this case the customer will be blacklisted and we will pass on relevent details to other vendors if we feel this is an attempt to defraud us. We are honest business people. (Multi-sig will only be a payment option on new markets until we build up trading history).


IMPORTANT: Payment Terms.

Because of the highly-volatile nature of BTC price and the massive fluctuations in value over short periods of time we require customers to pay for their orders when they are marked as dispatched thus enabling us to lock-in the price and protect ourselves from devaluations. We are also requiring FE to ensure we don t fall victim to escrow losses should the market go down permanently or for a long duration. Were sure youll understand this.


PLEASE NOTE: This will make no difference to you as a customer. Your BTC will pass directly to us instead of sitting in Escrow. Your order will be treated in exactly the same manner by us. We will however be able to cash-out at the day s rate thus receiving the correct FIAT payment.

OUR CANNABIS STRAINS

Wilkommen liebe Raucherinnen und Raucher,


ich bin nicht hier um der erfolgreichste Verkufer, oder die Nr.1 zu werden.

Hier wird meine berschssige Medizin (medizinisches Cannabis) zum Selbstkostenpreis angeboten!

Meine Pflanzen bekommen die Liebe und Aufmerksamkeit, die sie verdienen.

Die Damen werden ausschlielich auf Erde angebaut, bekommen nur feinste Bio Canna Produkte und werden 14 Tage vor der Ernte

mit klarem, PH- reguliertem Wasser gegossen, damit alle Nhrstoffe abgebaut werden. Das schmeckt man!

Die Buds werden direkt manikrrt, dann 3 oder 4 Tage aufgehangen und anschlieend reifen sie mindestens 4 Wochen im Glas,

bevor sie hier angeboten werden.

Es gibt fast immer bergewicht. Grade wenn es mir zu blttrig oder "klein" vorkommt, gleiche ich dies immer durch bergewicht aus.

Da bin ich absolut Fair.

Alle die ihre Adresse im Klartext mitteilen gehen ein extrem hohes Risiko ein negative Post zu bekommen wenn Serverdaten in

Falsche Hnde fallen, der Markt von falschen betrieben wird oder die Betreiber selber diese Daten weiterverkaufen.

MANUELLE Adressvorverschlsselung schafft abhifle, da sonst aller Schrift- und Adressverkehr mitgelesen werden kann.

Der Umgang mit PGP ist Pflicht geworden um sich von Zentralitt unabhngig zu machen.

Desweiteren knnt ihr auf den Vornamen verzichten oder abkrzen ("M. Mustermann"). Mich interessieren eure Daten sowieso nicht

aber da das sammeln von Daten bei fast allen Hndler "modern" ist, rate ich, so wenig wie mglich Preis zu geben. Auerdem knnt

ihr bei rger immer behaupten, dass ihr als "Drop" benutzt wurdet, denn es ist ja gar kein "Vorname" auf der Sendung.

Das Klingelschild sollte - wenn noch nicht geschehen ebenfalls angepasst werden.

Einfach Testsendung an sich selber schicken und schauen ob es ankommt.

We are a collective of cannabis-concentrate enthusiasts, the idea that this beautiful herb can be used to heal many ailments is why we are primarily in this business.
We are proud to be the caregivers for countless clients and always strive to better and refine our methods of extractions to ensure the highest level medicine for those suffering with ailments such as Crohns, MS, cancer patients etc.
At our humble shop we are mainly focused on RAW THC DISTILLATE but also provide Rick Simpsons Oil (RSO) and BHO extraction Shatter.
We also have some talented candy chefs who make the tastiest candies, gummy bears, taffy twists, rainbow belts soon!

If you have any queries that are not listed on the F.A.Q below please do not hesitate to message.
We very much hope you enjoy our wares!

F.A.Q

? CAN I USE RAW THC DISTILLATE IN VAPE CART ?

- Yes you can put our distillate directly into your vape cartridge, make sure its a CCELL otherwise the RAW distillate by itself will be too thicc to burn any other fake carts.

? DOES THIS COME FLAVORED OR HAVE A SMELL ?

- No we only stock RAW THC DISTILLATE at this time it has NO flavor or smell as it has no terpene profile, this is removed during short path distillation to ensure high quality THC produce only.
- You will need to buy your own terpenes, heat the distillate, mix 3-5% terpenes to the distillate and thoroughly stir, syringe up distillate then put into your cartridge.

SHIPPING F.A.Q

We send via first class non track mail only 
Orders are shipped within 24hours of being placed
Estimated delivery time is 1 to 5 days for UK domestic
Estimated delivery time is 8 to 21+ days for UK shipping worldwide depending on country ordering from

Were a team of growers committed to producing good quality cannabis for peoples medical and recreational needs. We focus more on strains that have strong medicinal value so in addition to some common Indicas and Sativas you will also find here some strains high in CBD that are excellent for helping to manage conditions like chronic pain, PTSD, anxiety, and more.

We dont use PGRs in our flowers and we make sure to dry and cure our buds so that they grind easily and smoke smoothly. We only list the harvests were happy with so you can be confident that everything on here is a quality product. 

We have a few strains on sale at the moment and will rotate regularly to provide a good range of products. If you dont find what youre looking for at the moment feel free to drop by again later on as we are growing new strains all the time.

Regards
Doctor Linnaeus
                

---------------


                    We aim to post orders the same day theyre received. We can only guarantee the posting of an item; we cannot guarantee the delivery. This is simply because sometimes packages can get lost in the post or significantly delayed due to Australias wonderful postal system. 

We can provide tracking details for express post orders however we cannot do so for standard post orders. If a standard post package is missing we cannot locate it and cannot confirm whether it has been delivered or not and as a result we will not re-ship standard packages. Your safest option is express.

Please note that we do not post orders on Friday, Saturday, or Sunday. We do not check orders on those days either. We process orders Monday through to Thursday only. If you questions or need to contact us please do so on those days. 

Please consider the weekend gap when ordering express as well. If you are outside of an express zone an express order posted on Thursday may not get to you until the following Monday or Tuesday, which is the equivalent of standard post time. If you need something quickly the best time to order is at the start of the week.

Welcome to DuhFarmers store. Were a longtime boutique indoor farmer selling high-quality, tested flower, with a dozen different strains currently available (and growing). We stand by our flowers and offer fantastic customer support! We also offer lower prices for larger orders, so if youre looking for bulk, let us know! First and Last Name, Street Number (address), Street Name, and then City, State/Country, Zip/Postal Code. And for international shipments, we need a destination phone number as well as the address.
Your flower will come bagged in separate, 1-oz (28.5g), vacuum-sealed bags. Each ounce is quadruple-bagged in three vacuum-sealed bags, and then heat-sealed into a scan-proof bag. In North America, orders usually arrive in 3-4 days, but sometimes can take as long as a week depending on weekends or holidays. For orders outside the US, expect it to arrive within 2-4 weeks.

In case of shipping problems:
To avoid scams, if an order is hung up in shipping, we will re-ship the same order for half price.
Thank you for working with us! If you enjoy our flowers half as much as we do, you will be very happy!

What is MDMA?

3,4-Methylenedioxymethamphetamine (also known as ecstasy, E, XTC, emma, molly, mandy, and MDMA) is a classical entactogen substance of the amphetamine class. MDMA is a derivative of the amphetamine family and is considered to be the prototype member of a diverse group of substances that includes MDA, methylone, and 6-APB, all of which act by increasing levels of neurotransmitters serotonin, dopamine, and norepinephrine in the brain. 


What are the effects of MDMA?

Subjective effects of MDMA include stimulation, anxiety suppression, disinhibition, enhanced empathy and sociability, relaxation, and euphoria.

Dissociative Anaesthetic; Psychedelic
CHEMICAL NAME
2-(2-chlorophenyl)-2-(methylamino)-cyclohexanone

Ketamine is a dissociative psychedelic used medically as a veterinary and human anaesthetic. It is one of the few addictive psychedelics and is associated with researcher John Lilly.
https://erowid.org/chemicals/ketamine/ketamine_faq.shtml

Psychedelic

d-lysergic acid diethylamide

benzoylmethyl ecgonine

3,4-methylenedioxymethamphetamine

A: Yes! We need to discuss the order and it may have to be voluntarily FE'd!

Q: I noted you also ship to packstations. What options are available?
A: If you need it tracked, select the parcel shipping option. If you select the standard shipping option we will ship that order as a letter.

Q: What if something goes wrong? What will happen then?
A: We discuss this on a case by case basis. In general we do not do refunds, but (partial) reships. NOTE: solutions will only be offered to people who contact us first, instead of leaving negative feedbacks or opening disputes. We are very lenient and easy to work with and are happy to provide any help needed.

Q: What happens if i open a dispute?
A: Then it will be up to a moderator to decide what happens. This can take currently up to several months. We reserve the right to blacklist you from our business and partners in the meantime and thereafter. Luckily it hardly ever comes to that. We are happy to help anyone out with a problem as quickly as possible. A happy customer = happy vendor!

Q: I have had some issues in the past so my buyer history shows that i have been in several disputes. Can i still order?
A: It depends on several factors! We decide this on a case by case basis. It also helps if you let us know upfront what exactly happened in the PGP address box.

Q: How do i send in my address? What is the correct format?
A: You can check this up on a website called addressdoctor.

Q: How fast do you actually ship.. and how many days does it take to arrive?
A: Very fast! We know people want their good as quickly as possible so we strive to ship everything within hours! Arrival time is depending on the postal service obviously but quickly shipped means usually quickly delivered. And we like to measure our delivery times in hours not days! European orders can arrive within 48 hours. Most domestic shipments arrive in 16-24 hours!

Q: I am worried about my security. What measures do you take to ensure no data is being saved or at risk?
A: Security is our very first priority. We work with encryption for our transactions and after addresses have been printed, they will be discarded. This is not only for the security of our customers but also for ourselves. Keeping records means it would be possible to trace back transactions and that would be a very bad and stupid thing for a vendor to do.

Q: What about packaging and stealth?
A: Our letters and parcels are disguised either as business communications or purchases from regular shops. That being said, we are very creative and rotate our packaging all the time. Our stealth is based on being able to blend it with millions of other pieces of mail.

Q: Should i use a fake name?
A: NO! Postal workers are required to deliver at correct addresses with the correct names! So make sure the name you supply matches the name on the mailbox! Otherwise it will most likely NOT arrive.

Q: What if i use an address where nobody lives or a friends house?
A: Very bad idea! Because the postal workers are again required to deliver mail as addressed! They will not just deliver your package. In fact, they will return your mail for investigation and try to find the real addressee which means they will most likely open the package in search for a packing slip or something. They will see the contents eventually and call the police. So don't do it!

Q: I am getting a message that i am restricted from buying products at this store! Why and how do i get around it?
A: This is because some shoppers let orders auto-finalize. Obviously this is very bad for business as we work hard to get orders out as quickly as possible. It's just a bad habit and as such we blacklist these users. To get around this you need to create a new account. But you will lose any freebies and extra's you would have gotten, if you finalized in a timely manner!

### Unsere Geschaeftsbedingungen ###

Lest euch bitte unser Profil komplett durch bevor Ihr etwas aus unserem Shop bestellt. Durch eure Bestellung akzeptiert ihr automatisch unsere nachfolgenden Bedingungen und Konditionen.

### Kontakt ###

Bei Fragen und Problemen koennt ihr uns jederzeit kontaktieren. Wir werden eure Mails schnellstmoeglich beantworten.
Falls Ihr mit eurer Bestellung einmal unzufrieden seid kontaktiert uns bitte bevor ihr eine schlechte Bewertung abgebt. Wir nehmen eure Anliegen ernst und versuchen gemeinsam eine Loesung fuer das Problem zu finden.

### Versand ###

Wir verschicken unsere Waren vorerst nur nach Deutschland. Der Versand innerhalb von EU-Laendern ist geplant. Aus Sicherheitsgruenden verschicken wir unsere Waren ausschlielich ohne Tracking. Alle Bestellungen werden Werktags innerhalb von 24 bis 48 Stunden verschickt dabei betraegt die Dauer der Zustellung 2-7 Werktage (Erfahrungsgemae 1-3 Tage).

Bitte gebt eure Adresse im folgenden Format an:

Vorname Nachname
Strae und Hausnummer
Postleitzahl und Ort

Bitte achtet darauf eure vollstaendige und richtige Adresse anzugeben damit die Sendungen auch zugestellt werden kann. Bei Nichtzustellung von Paketen aufgrund von falschen oder unvollstaendigen Adressen uebernehmen wir keine Haftung.

### Verpackung/Lieferung ###

All unsere Waren werden ordnungsgemae verpackt und versiegelt sodass der Eindruck einer gewoehnlichen legalen Shop-Bestellung garantiert ist. Die Ware wird in sicheren Luftpolstertaschen versendet die in eure Briefkaesten hinterlegt wird. Bei Bestellungen von groeeren Mengen (ueber 200ml) wird der Versand aus Sicherheitsgruenden in zwei Sendungen aufgeteilt. Die dadurch entstehenden Mehrkosten tragen wir als Verkaeufer.

Nach Versand der Ware werden alle Kundendaten umgehend vernichtet!

Wir nehmen nur Bestellungen von verschluesselten Adressen an. Bitte verwendet hierfuer ausschlielich PGP!

### Falls mal was verloren geht ###

Fuer den Fall dass Sendungen einmal nicht zugestellt wurden gewaehren wir euch einen Reship/Refund in BTC unter folgenden Bedingungen:

1) Re-Ship/Refund von 50%: mindestens 1 erfolgreiche Bestellung wurde bei uns getaetigt.
2) Re-Ship/Refund von 100%: mindestens 2 erfolgreiche Bestellungen wurden bei uns getaetigt.

Bei einer Erstbestellung koennen wir leider keinen Re-Ship/Refund anbieten.

### Escrow ###

Bitte vergesst nicht eure Bestellungen abschlieend zu finalisieren sobald ihr eure Ware erhalten habt damit unsere Coins nicht ewig im Escrow haengen bleiben.

### Feedback ###

Wenn Ihr mit der Ware zufrieden seid wuerden wir uns sehr ueber ein positives Feedback freuen.

I'm happy to continue to deliver my Ultra Clean LSD. Each hit is approximately 150ug. This is the same great acid which has been available on Agora and Dream for the last couple years. It is a clean clear crystal and I strive to continue to supply some of the best LSD on the DNMs. Lab tested, Hippie approved, you'll be sure to have a nice trip. 

Why is this the best LSD in the world?
Not all LSD is created equally.  This crystal is made in the tradition of Owsley and is refined to the highest standards, it is truly pharmacalogical grade. It melts the second it touches alcohol and dissolves 100%. Fluff and needlepoint are good stuff, typically around 91-97% of that crystal dissolves in alcohol and  they would be my next choice.  Careful though, some of the crap that sells on the DNMs is cut so much that many of the dealers reselling that can say and might even think thier hits are (X)ugs but really they should multiply that by about 0.8 or less because they are more than likely only getting that much pure LSD by wieght.  That is still better than the "champaigne" crystal which is tan-brown-red.  Champaigne skips the whole last step in purification and is only like 70-74%, some even lower.  Watch out for that stuff, its cheap for a reason.  One of the important things about "family" crystal, this ultra pure, or the less refined fluff, originates at the very beginning process with the cultivation of particular ergotamine strains.  These strains have been passed down through the generations and the research and lineage has been being perfected since the days of Albert Hoffman, who spent years isolating strains of the mold.  Different strains create different effects and feelings when the finished product is ingested. New producers just can't match the history and quality when it comes to the basic building blocks.  That's why dead heads usually have the best stuff, it is the tradition behind the production.  It is alleged that once upon a time a two archeologists were exploring an Egyptian tomb and found two seplecures, one containing ergotamine and one containing rye.  Supposedly one of those archeologists was the first modern case of ergotamine poisoning, the other took the seplecures to Albert Hoffman and the rest was history.  I am honored to take part in this tradition and proud to provide this high quality product to you all.
=========================================================
SHIPPING -
All orders packed with MBB.
All cannabis orders are domestic only.
Cannabis orders are over listed weight.
Cannabis orders are double vacuum sealed, washed, then sealed with MBB.
All domestic orders are tracked priority.
"Strain Highlights" are quoted from leafly.
Most orders arrive within 3-7 business days from order date. 

==========================================================
TRACKING - 
Tracking will be made available upon request one week after being marked "shipped".  (Extended to 14 days during December because Christmas extends shipping times)  When "accepted" they typically go out within 48 hours. Orders accepted on the weekend won't typically ship until Monday. No one wants a box of weed to sit in a post box all weekend.  For faster service on tracking info requests please include name, address, and order date with your tracking info requests. I can't link directly from your profile to your order and this makes it much easier for me to look up and double check for anything that may have caused a delay or mistake.  
This is not Amazon and safety, not speed, is my priority.  I don't claim to do any next day shipping or anything like that but orders are often shipped the next day.  The reason I have a one week tracking policy is that if I give tracking to someone and they are some sort of cop, they could use that information to find other orders and do controlled deliveries on other customers. Also, if the site is hacked or monitored by LE sending tracking info could also give them vital customer information. This policy is for the safety of all my customers and I hope you all can understand that.  I have done thousands of orders and you would be surprised how often USPS priority actually take 5 business days to get there.  Typically, when I give someone tracking they end up getting the package the next day anyhow.  So the policy is a week from shipped date, we can start to suspect something has possibly gone wrong. Until then, please be patient.
=========================================================
INFORMED DELIVERY -
Lately more people are using informed delivery and asking why packages say shipped but haven't showed up on there.  I don't print postage from usps or take the orders into the branch in person so it doesn't necessarily show up on your informed delivery so please don't message about informed delivery if your order is marked shipped it is on the way.
===============================================================
REFUND POLICY - 
No refunds if tracking says "Delivered".
If there is no "Delivery" for some reason then refund or reship determined on case by case basis.
==========================================================
FINALIZATION -
FE not always required but always appreciated.  If you take advantage of an escrow offer, please log on and finalize once you have received your order.  Timely finalization helps me keep escrow open for everyone as there are limits to what I can risk having on the site at any given time.  I am still available for customer support whether or not your order is finalized.

Lux cartridges are pure, potent, and safe. That's been our goal since day one, and we feel like we achieve that objective with every cart we sell.
We start by using the best distillate we can possibly source. Biodynamically grown marijuana, free of pesticides, is distilled multiple times to remove impurities. There is cheap distillate out there, and then there's the good stuff. Our distillate is beautifully clear and pure. It doesn't discolor with age, and it vapes smooth and easy.
Then we add 5% terpenes. Our proprietary terpene blends are organic, non-GMO, and vegan. We do not use any syntheic terpenes.
That's it. We do not use any PG, VG, PEG, MCT, or any other diluant. We have certainly never used any shady "thickening" agents. Our bubble doesn't move because our carts are 95% THC distillate, 5% organic terpenes, and nothing else.
We use high-end (and expensive!) cart hardware that is manufactured exclusively for us. The carts themselves cost around $2.00 each and are not any sort of knockoff. The borosilicate glass tank is laser-engraved with the LUX logo as a sign of quality.
We are quite proud of our reputation, and honestly do care about our product and our customers. We use our own product every day, and we believe in "doing well by doing good". We want to make money, for sure. Lime green Bentleys don't buy themselves. But we would never put profit ahead of our customers' health or happiness.
Buy Lux vape cartridges with confidence. Experience for yourself their pure, potent, and safe high. We think you'll be glad you did!

We are big believers in the healing power of CBD.  Pure THC cartridges don't contain a measurable amount of CBD.  Even leaf marijuana contains only a tiny amount.  There are hemp strains, though, that have been bred to contain a high percentage of CBD.
That's why we created MAGIC POTION.
It's a combination of 50% THC distillate and 50% full-spectrum CBD distillate. This product does not contain terpenes but exhibits a rich cannabis flavor from the CBD distillate.  We use extremely high-quality CBD distillate with about a 90% purity.  It's full-spectrum which means it contains many other cannabinoids found in the hemp plant as well.
This is an especially beneficial product for anybody suffering from anxiety, stress, chronic pain, or sleep problems.
Note that this mix is pure distillate on both sides, so it can't be classified as an indica, sativa, or hybrid. It will produce a well-balanced high with the physical full-body relief associated with high potency CBD. 
Give it a try, I think you will be amazed!

You shouldn't.  Ever. Receiving a small parcel in the mail is only sketchy if you make it sketchy.
Here's what you do:
If your mom isn't going to open all your mail: Mail it to your home. Everybody here has good stealth. It's going to be fine.
If your mom is going to open all your mail: Use a PO Box. We ship to them all the time with no issues. Most places they're only like $20 a month.
Don't use a fake name.  Mail carriers are well aware who lives at a particular residence. In my case, they even put a little sticker on the inside of my mailbox with my last name on it.  Using a fake name doesn't give you "plausible deniability", it causes your mail carrier to really extra super scrutinize your pack.
Don't use a neighbor's house. You're going to oversleep and forget to check their mail and they're going to get a package of drugs that was obviously ordered by their stoner-ass neighbor and the shit will hit the fan.
Don't use a vacant house.  Duh. When people move they fill out change-of-address forms. Your drugs are going to get forwarded to the Pattersons at their new home in Tulsa.
Repeat:
Receiving a package in the mail isn't sketchy until you make it sketchy.

Lamp Updates

Aug 24
Hello Empire friends, we are here to welcome all of you to WHM. We believe this market to have much higher security standards. All communication must be encrypted It takes some getting used to but is well worth it in the long run, trust. All of our prices here relfect what was on Empire, but if you require a quantity not listed please feel free to message us or calculate using next tier down pricing and buy tipjar listing. e.g. User wants to purchase 7g crumble, 5g/$75 listing would be used to calculate $15/g and $105+$12 shipping. $117 in tipjar with notes indicating order. Welcome to WHM!

FAQ

* What is your potency THC/CBD levels on Insert product here??
I can't currently confirm the potency on any of my products mainly because I swap them out so rapidly it would not make sense for me to try and keep track of this. If you are concerned feel free to send any of my products off to a testing company and provide me with documented results and proof of payment to them and I will compensate you with product on your next order.

* Can you split my order into half one strain and half another? Yes strain splits(or wax order splits) are acceptable of 56g+ orders. Please limit splits to increments of 28g. Items split must be at same price points. For cart splits we ask you keep it to 4 minimum so for orders of 8 you are allowed two choices. For orders of less please keep it to one strain. For artisan waxes we ask splits to be kept in minimum of 3gram increments for shatters and bulk waxes we ask you to keep splits to 28grams as mentioned earlier.

* I'm a little low on funds can I send you below the advertised prices you have?
My prices are set at the absolute rock bottom minimum that still allows me to stay in business and I dont plan on raising them any higher unless people keep asking me if they can short me 10$. If you're 50cents short dont worry about it if it's more than a few bucks just wait for BTC price to flucuate as it has been for quite a while now up.

* How often do you change strains? For flower one or two gets added or deleted every month or so. For oil it varries based on material availability and can be quite frequent and stocks of some specialized waxes can be fairly lower. Ask about stock if curious.

* At this time we choose to keep all orders domestic sorry foreign friends.

* HELP I placed an order a super long time ago and haven't received it?! Pause take a deep breath friend. I will do EVERYTHING in my power to make sure you are a satisfied customer and get what you deserve. I am not in the business of ripping people off and that is not what I enjoy doing. Send me what you ordered when you ordered and your address ALL encrypted using PGP. Give me some time for a response and I will either respond with tracking for you to check or will have a different resolution.

Shipping

* We ship orders M-F and typically take 1-2 days to process. If placed before 3pm PST your order will likely go out next day some may even make it out same day. USPS Priority is 2-5days despite what USPS claims. Tracking will very rarely be provided if I feel the need for the breech of OPSEC necessary for your convenience then it will only be provided upon our discretion.

*COMBINED SHIPPING - 
-Please note combined flower and extract orders DO NOT qualify at this time. Please pay shipping on both.
If you use this option please do so wisely or it will add a delay to your order. Your FIRST order should be paid in full with shipping. Every subsequent order can use the combined shipping option if reasonable(check with us for large flower distillate and edible orders). If you do use combined shipping we ask you use the SAME fee and place all orders within 5minutes of each other. This ensures they all arrive at the same time on our end and that none of your orders get stuck in queue and dont make it out as a result.

* Use a tool like Smarty Streets to verify your address and send it to us in a proper ENCRYPTED format.

* PLEASE ONLY USE A REAL ADDRESS ALL FAKE ADDRESS ORDERS WILL BE CANCELED.

Refund Policy

50% reship in case of missing pack 100% reship in case of seizure for delivered status tracking but claim of no pack it is up to discretion of vendor

Magic Lamp Guarantee

We aim to please every customer to the highest satisfaction possible whether your order is big or small. If there is any problems with your order we will do everything in our power to obtain a happy satisfied customer. We take business very seriously and even more importantly we take providing medicine as a serious responsibility that has been gifted to us.

Please be aware that Canada Post has been giving regular notices that they are seeing volumes never seen before and they are extremely delayed. As a reference, Xpresspost orders are regularly taking longer then a week to arrive instead of the usual 1-3 days so I wouldn't even want to guess the time frames on standard mail. If you live in Canada and would like your package in any reasonable amount of time I would strongly suggest choose the express shipping option as these will take priority in the mail stream.

To all my long time and loyal client, I have done an assessment of my business model and will be moving away from carrying Schedule I substances under Canadian law given how much better LE is at finding vendors online.

Welcome to the MedDoctors Lab.

Who are we?
MedDoctors are new to the BM but not to the industry. We are a group of highly experienced growers/connoisseurs  from the UK. 

We have over 10 years experience in growing weed and are proud of what we produce. You will not find any higher quality cannabis than our top shelf organic.

We know this is high on price but we will still lose out on this method  of growing overall (except for with the smoke) ;) as the yield is so much lower than using coco feeds. This is what we personally prefer to smoke when possible.

We try to have something  for everyone with our range but unfortunately at the moment we are more high end due to having some of the most rare strains on the market. We will have some more common strains to offer soon, with lower prices.

What do we do?
We are known for growing top quality product with no exceptions. We have a variety of different strains which have took a lot of time and effort to find and to perfect.

They are all tried and tested by ourselves before sale (perks of the job) :). We take pride in what we do and can guarantee our customers will see this in our end result.  

Methods of growing?

COCO-  70% of our weed is grown using coco and fed minimum feed as possible while still maintaining dense nugs at the end of the flower period. They are then flushed for at least 10days before going through the drying process which we prolong as much as possible. Every step is to ensure a clean smoke and white ash that all connoisseurs look for. 

HOMEMADE ORGANIC- The other 30% of our weed is grown using a homemade soil with a feed consisting of a compost tea (good bacteria) plus a few of our own homemade organic secrets ;). We really believe this product can not be beaten in taste and overall smoke.(CALIGRADE)

All of our weed is cured for at least a month in glass jars before sold. (many a lot longer)

* Top quality product

MercuryXPR Dead Drops

The dead drop program is aimed at decreasing the time it requires a customer to obtain their item.

Dead drops are available as a shipping option on orders of 1.75 grams and larger of dmeth, 1 grams or larger of cocaine or heroin and 3.5g or more of MDMA moonrocks.

The program works as follows. Should you wish to order an item where dead drop is listed as an shipping option simply proceed through the checkout process as normal however just include a note in the address field regarding your desire for a dead drop.

FAQ

Q: Can I have the tracking info for my package? A: Yes - but not before the item is officially late - which is three business days for ExpressPost, five business days for ParcelPost and five business days for Priority. Note that this does not include the date of order.

Greetings and welcome. We are pleased to offer personal-use amounts of marijuana, hashish, cannabis concentrates and edibles, and psychedelics, packed carefully and shipped quickly. All orders ship from the Southeastern United States, far from the drug source states of California, Oregon, and Colorado.
The ModernLove Team has been active on the Darknet since the days of the original Silk Road, where we operated with the username PowerToCharm. We also vended on SR2, Cannabis Road, Evolution, BlackBank, Agora, Abraxas, Dream Market, Samsara, and CGMC until the demise of each of those markets, and we are now very pleased to be active on CannaHome. Our PGP public key is below, and has been the same since SR2. Please feel free to send us an encrypted message to verify our identity. We look forward to serving our old customers, and getting to know many new ones.
Alternate contact if the site is down: modernlove[at]elude[dot]in
Please note that we are currently active only on CannaHome, Empire, and Apollon. Anyone claiming to be ModernLove on any other market is an impostor and almost certainly a scammer.

We ship a minimum of four days each week, using a rotating pattern to avoid establishing a predictable schedule. Saturdays are included in the rotation. If your order status shows "shipped," this means that the item has left our facility and been dropped in a USPS collection box. Depending upon the collection time for that particular box, it's possible that your order might sit in the box overnight and begin its journey the following morning.
We only ship to addresses within the United States, including Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands. We do not ship to APO/FPO addresses.
It is very important that you provide a VALID AND ACCURATE SHIPPING ADDRESS. Please check, and check again, to make sure your address is correct.
All orders ship via USPS with tracking, though for security reasons tracking numbers are generally not provided to buyers. If you believe that your shipment is late or lost, we are happy to check the tracking for you.

Full or partial refunds are offered on a situation-specific basis. If tracking shows that your item was delivered, no refund will be offered. If tracking shows your item is undeliverable because of an error in the shipping address you provided, no refund will be offered.

We accept bitcoin for payment, submitted through the CannaHome payment platform. We will not do off-market or direct deals; please don't ask.
As a matter of principle and policy, we never request or require direct pay (aka early finalization). At the same time, we do have some justifiable apprehension about the volatility of bitcoin and the stability of darkweb markets. PLEASE FINALIZE PROMPTLY once you receive your order. Thank you.

about:

I have been growing mushrooms for a long time.  Mushrooms are grown inside a clean semi-greenhouse automated environment with all organic ingredients. 
Mushrooms are never touched by human hands. The isolates offered where chosen as superior over a large array of genetics i have grown in the past. Qualities I aim for include trip quality, potency, and appearance.  
Check out the rest of my profile for more detail about whats being offered.

Updated DEC 17th
This is a short description of my small library of genetics.  I don't keep all isolates in stock at the same time:
 Classic Penis Envy  Dosage: 
Microdose = 50 - 70 Milligrams - give or take 10 mg
MiniDose  = 'About' .5 Grams
moderate trip = 1.5 Gram
Strong Trips Start at 'about' 2- 2.5 Grams
Effects:
1.  Penis Envy Isolate C - Hydbrid effects -strong head and body - classic mushroom high - comfortable microdoses - good for anxiety. Out of stocK, next harvest 2 or 3 weeks away(max).  
2.  Penis Envy Isolate A - Strong cerebral effects, minimal body effects -clean electric high - makes for a very happy day time microdose. good for depression.  Out of stocK, next harvest 2 or 3 weeks away(max).  
 Albino Penis Envy  Dosage: 
Microdose = 40 - 60 Milligrams - give or take 10 mg
MiniDose  = 'About' .4 Grams
moderate trip = 1 Gram
Strong Trips Start at 'about' 1.5 - 2 Grams
1.  Albino Penis Isolate A1 - very strong cerebral/head high, light body effects.  Excellent for depression.  May not be best for anxiety; thoughts may race a bit. IN STOCK
2.  Albino Penis Envy Isolate A2 - Strong body effects.  Great for meditation dose.  Also excellent for microdosing if battling anxiety -easy social interactions with proper microdose.  OUT OF STOCK  - Available in about 1 month.
All isolate descriptions where accumulated from tons of reports, reviews, questioning, and personal experience.

Why isolates:
Mushrooms are like humans. You are a single isolated human being; a unique combination of genetics which are a part of your family tree.  Like humans, mushrooms have a base range of possible personalites/effects.     
I came to realize the extreme important of isolates some years back.  I had -this one batch- of penis envy mushrooms that consistenly gave all who consumed them; very dark trips.
About isolates:
Mushroom culture isolates give yield, potency, and "trip quality" uniformity across all grows initiated with that culture.  This is to make sure the mushrooms you had from me 4 years ago, will be the exact same mushrooms years later.
A sporeprint from a mushroom can contain hundreds of thousands of microscopic spores.  Each pairing, or group of pairings, produce noticably different effects. Traditionally, mycologist select the pairing of genetics which give the largest yield of pretty mushrooms with good potency. I take it one step further, I also focus on effects.  
Why I offer different isolates of the same strain:
The isolation process is simple but time consuming.  When working with a culture on a agar plate, it naturally seperate and sector mycellium into somewhat even sectors of unique genetics. A petri dish with a mushroom culture on it will look like a sliced pizza pie.  Each one of those slices represent unique mushroom genetics.  My job when isolating is to seperate all slices of mycellium on the petri dish, grow them out -one by one -then test their effects, aestetics and yield.        
 I currently have a collection of four distinct Isolated cultures.  Some of these isolates took up to 6 months. The task of selecting, dosing, and saving dozens of isolates per strain isn't a fast process, but it's well worth the effort.
Mushroom Isolate/personality:
Some Isolates give an intense body buzz, others give a very trippy energetic high - while the rest may be in the middle; a hybrid of effects.
  I'm not sure why mushrooms aquire these particular effect qualities.  Is it the unique ratio of alkaloids? or Maybe like cannabis -the trip quality relates to the amount and ratio of unique terpenes each phenotype contain? -maybe it's a combination? 
 I notice this about the isolates offered; the broad cap wider stem mushroom cultures are moreso body trip oriented; the skinnier -more narrow capped cultures lean more towards a cerebral trip. ;-)

Shipping:
Use first and last name - no initials
Orders are shipped mon - thur, usually next day,sometimes two days if very busy.
Once marked shipped,expect package within 3 days -not including Fri Sat and Sunday.
If order is not received after the 4th day in transit, message me so tracking information isn't destroyed. Customer information is deleted 1 week after expected delivery.
Policy:
All orders are properly packaged with tracking. In the event a order goes missing you will receive a full refund or reship. No refund will be given if tracking displays item as delivered. No refund will be given if buyer provides a undeliverable address or fake name.

If youre still with us by now, we appreciate it! 

Since we prioritise in customer service, we think you should know, who you are buying from. 
You will notice that we take our business very seriously, but we also appreciate a good sense of humour, therefore you will probably detect some jokes here and there. 

We were actually planning our comeback on Berlusconi and Samsara, but since Berlusconi is gone, and Samsara doesnt seem to get its Ddos Attacks under control, these options opted out. Also Empire is so overwhelming, that you feel like on an oriental bazaar, not knowing where to look and where to buy.

So we decided to have our comeback here at Appollon, because we think it has the potential to become the next big thing.


So lets begin with a (quick) introduction of our team.

We are four individuals, who used to sell very successfully on alphabay and silkroad. Through ordering bulks from each other regularly, we started becoming good friends and shared our precious sources with one another. 

After taking some time off the web, we finally decided to get back to what we can do best and enjoy most: making our customers happy and high. 

And this time were coming with a new and better system: we are working as a team. Besides, this time were having access to the infamous Golden Triangle of South-East Asia.

Three of our members are each located in the Netherlands, Germany and the UK, therefore we ship from these three countries, but we also ship to all other European countries!

Our products are all exactly the same, but we will ship your orders depending on your shipping address, so youll receive them as fast as possible! That means, if you live in Germany, youll get your order shipped FROM Germany .. and so on. 

Our fourth member (me - the one writing this text) moved to Asia two years ago and is the key to the Opium Golden-Triangle. I do have other tasks in this store though, but Ill start with introducing my dear friends first. 

Each country has its own representative, that will take good care of your Highness. 

John Travolta - Netherlands

- Hes responsible for all our dutch customers and shippings. Although he moved there 4 years ago, everyone still keeps talking to him in English, so his Dutch is not the best. Anyway hes trying to learn, so feel free to write him in Dutch, but hell probably reply in English. 


Samuel L. Jackson - Germany 

- Hes taking care of our German customers and orders. He DOES speak German. Very well actually. But since there is barely anything Samuel L. Jackson CANT do, its not really surprising, is it?


Bruce Willis - United Kingdom

- Bruce is our guy for the UK. Hes also your contact man, if youre being held hostage by a pathetic, cowardly rapist. He will bring a gun and let you shoot. 


And me: Quentin Tarantino - Rest of Europe 

I am basically the director of PulpFiction, but I also play a supporting role. 

- I take care of all our other European customers. I decide from which country your order will be shipped, so you receive it as fast as possible. I also speak German and a little french and spanish, if youre more comfortable with that. 
- If you have a preference, you can decide yourself from which of the 3 countries you want your order to be shipped from. Just write it below your shipping address: PLEASE SHIP FROM NETHERLANDS (for example). 
- Otherwise I will decide, where you will get your order from, based on the experience we have with the shipping times to different countries.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SHIPPING INFO

For your own safety please encrypt all your shipping addresses with our Public Key! We NEVER safe any adresses!!!

ALL SHIPPINGS ARE FREE!
Consider us as the DN version of Amazon Prime. 

We ship from Monday to Friday. If you order before 2pm, we will ship it the same day. 

ESTIMATED shipping times (working days):

Germany: 1-4 days
Netherlands: 1-4 days
UK: 1-4 days 
Belgium: 1-4 days
Luxembourg: 1-4 days
France: 2-6 days
Spain: 2-6 days
Portugal: 2-6 days
Scandinavia: 3-6 days
Other countries: 2-7 days

Please contact us first, if your order does not arrive in the estimated shipping time. Unfortunately we cannot influence the post office workers, and since we are offering free shipping, we can't tell the exact destination of the order. We will only get notified as soon as it arrives in your mailbox.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


We actually think, you probably know how to phrase your shipping address correctly, but since every vendor here seems to show how its done, we dont want to miss out on the trend. So here are some examples. 


NETHERLANDS

Vincent Van Gogh
Tweede Weteringplantsoen 21
1017 ZD Amsterdam
Netherlands


GERMANY

Christoph Waltz
Schlossalllee 1
13156, Berlin
Germany


UNITED KINGDOM

Daniel Radcliffe
4 Temple Row W
Birmingham B2 5NY
United Kingdom


REST OF EUROPE

Just write your standard shipping address for your country, but make sure to name your country at the bottom!!!

Also as said, if you want to order from a specific country, please let us know!


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

REFUND & RESHIP

We rarely had any issues with our deliveries, but we know that the post can always mess stuff up. So if we get notified that your order couldnt be send to your shipping address and has returned to the post office, we will reship for FREE.

However if we get notified that the order has reached your place, but somehow you say, its not in your mailbox (which is really rare), we will discuss the case, and if you seem trustworthy we will reship at least 50%. 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If you have any further questions, dont hesitate to contact us.

PulpFictionStore@protonmail.com

Since were four people, any of us will surely reply within a couple of hours if you write us an E-Mail, since we can check that more regularly. 

If you write us on the market we will definitely reply within 24 hours.

your Pulp Fiction Team

DMT Consumption Guide:
Smoking DMT for the first time can be a challenge. That is why I put together a list of all possible consumption methods.
There are a set of rules one should follow to get the best out of it.

DOSAGE:

The beautiful thing about DMT is that it is not possible to overdose on it (DMT starts to become poisonous at about 6g). Don't be afraid of taking a bit too much. When asked, most people will say 50mg is the correct amount. The truth is that it varies from person to person and that the technique is crucial. If you manage to vaporize 30mg correctly without burning anything you might have a stronger experience than with 50mg poorly handled DMT.
50mg is a good start nontheless and the amount I recommend to all beginners because it leaves room for mistakes. If it still does not work out, take the experience with you and don't give up. Be relaxed. It's a journey and you learn a lot on the way.

Once you become an experienced journeyer you can start using larger amounts of DMT to get deeper into the realm. The experience of 70mg+ can be overwhelming if you take DMT for the first time but once you get used to it you will no longer be afraid.

SETTING:

The setting is very important. Be in a calm place where you are certain that nothing unexpected will happen. People randomly coming in and things like that can ruin the trip.
In case you live in a noisy environment it's a good idea to use headphones and ambient/soothing music.
Make sure you feel absolutely safe. Anything that bothers you should be removed. Don't do it anywhere where you think you can feel scared or annoyed once you are tripping.
It is important that it's very quiet. Only nice sounds are allowed (birds, waves etc). If you do it with someone else, they must shut the hell up! The only exception to that is when someone whispers into your ear to induce thoughts into your trip. That person should be experienced though.

For inspiration: On my first trip I was on a beach on sunset. My boyfriend at the time held the pipe for me and told me exactly what to do. I trusted him completely and after I was on the other side I felt the warmth of his presence.

TECHNIQUES:

If your favorite technique is not included in this guide, shoot me a message!

The smoking techniques are very important as DMT needs to be evaporated. It shouldn't be burned because that would destroy the effects. You know the DMT is evaporated when you feel a hot sensation in your throat. If your technique is correct the DMT will be completely tasteless. If it's harsh it's because you burned some DMT. Even if you get the harsh taste just continue.

Inhalation: Once the DMT is evaporated you need to start  inhaling deeply and slowly until you can't keep going any more.  Hold your breath for at least 10 seconds. Do it as long as possible. Else you will waste DMT once you exhale.

Take as many hits as you need to break through. Usually it's 2-3. With a good technique and a little experience you will become able to breakthrough after one single hit.
If you do not break through all you will feel is a slight buzz and maybe some light hallucinations.

Important: If you fail you have to wait at least 1 hour before trying again, else you will just fail again as the body needs to recover.

If you are intimidated by DMT and wish to start slow you can inhale 15mg and slowly increase the amount until you finally break through. There is no shame in that.


No matter which method you end up choosing, be careful to hold your device in such a way that no liquid DMT can get out. The taste is very bad. Trust me, you don't want to know.
If you are going to do DMT regularly, get a dedicated device as the taste will never go away again.

The boiling point of DMT is 160 C (320 F). You should use more energy in for a clean evaporation though.

Vaporizer: If you use a vaporizer the temperature should be set to around 230C or 450F. Depending on your vaporizer the temperature setting may vary. If the DMT turns liquid but does not boil and evaporate, try raising the temperature by 10% until it works.

Pen Vaporizers: Simply load your DMT into the chamber, activate and inhale once the DMT is evaporated. This is a very simple method and often results in a one hit break through.

Pipes/Bongs: For beginners the general rule is that if you are going to torch it, the flame must not touch the crystals.
Have some sort of buffer between the flame and the crystals, like a layer of ashes. If the flame touches the crystals, a lot will get wasted
For the same reason the crystals should not touch the bottom of your pipe or bong.
There should be a layer of something like a bit of weed or some herbs or even some ashes to protect the crystals from heat.

Once you are more advanced you might get the hang of torching it just right so it evaporates even without any sort of buffer. It looks cool too!

Joints: Another method is smoking it with a joint. Yes, it does work if done correctly. Sprinkle the DMT crystals opposite to the end you will burn. The hot air will evaporate the Dream Sand as you inhale slowly and gradually. This method is not very precise and you might need to add a little more DMT than you would with the other methods.

Oil rigs: Torch the nail until it is hot red, then count roughly 25 seconds so the nail is nice and evenly hot at the right temperature. Then dab the nail into the DMT and start inhaling. If you get a harsh taste the nail needs to cool off a little longer. If the DMT does not evaporate you need to shorten the cool off time.

The Machine: There is a big fanbase around this device. It is essentially a selfmade vaporizer made of a glass bottle and steel wool. You can find a detailed construction guide here: hxxps://www.dmt-nexus.me/forum/default.aspx?g=posts&t=25974

The trick is to first melt the DMT into the steel mesh. You do this by sprinkling your DMT dose on the mesh.
1. approaching a flame ( I tilt the bottle in 45 degrees so the DMT will not fall off and melt) under the neck of the bottle with regular lighter from a distance of 4-5cm 1.5-2inch until the DMT melts.
2. Another method that people use is to heat the neck of the bottle (bottle stand vertically) with torch lighter until DMT  is melted.
Now you are ready to begin taking your hits. Hold the flame near the mesh and slowly inhale through the mouth hole. You should see the flame being sucked towards the mesh as you inhale. Make sure the flame doesn't touch the mesh, keep it about an inch or 1.5 cm away. The idea is to evaporate the DMT by convection (hot air), not conduction.

E-cigarette: 1ml liquid is good for about 500mg DMT. Just mix them together and wait for a day for the DMT to fade away.
Best to use about 2g of DMT with 3 to 5ml and use a low dosage of mint flavor liquid to cancel out the plastic taste of DMT. 
Evaporate at 10-15 Watts so the DMT does not get burned. With those dosages you will need about 4-5 hits and then you will be in hyperspace.

SFTreats is here to deliver the finest bud from the San Francisco Bay Area straight to your door!

We aim to cultivate the highest quality top shelf indoor hydroponic medical cannabis available. Every plant is sourced from the best boutique clones available and given tremendous love and technical attention over it's life-cycle. Before harvest, each pot is flushed of all impurities and nutrients for ten to fourteen days to purify the natural flavors. Once harvested, every bud is immaculately trimmed by careful, skilled hands; we never use a machine. None of our medicine is ready for use until it has dried for a week and cured for two additional weeks at a minimum.

From us, you will get it all: bag appeal, a huge bouquet of stank, exquisite flavors, high-octane performance, plenty of margin if you hook up your pals - delivered promptly and securely, with consistent, reliable, and friendly service.

I DO NOT SHIP TO CALIFORNIA
I DO NOT SHIP INTERNATIONALLY

We ship three days a week. Monday, Wednesday, and Saturday. Delivery is expected within 3 days anywhere in the US, including Hawaii. Most deliveries occur within 2 days from shipping.

All packages are sent in small, medium, or large USPS Priority Mail Flat Rate boxes.

Every box has a printed Stamps.com label, complete with tracking, and show up on My USPS. No ghetto stamps.

We do not vacuum seal your weed, as to not crush delicate buds.

The first layer of protection is a Ziploc Mylar dispensary bag like Smelly Proof or Stink Sack.This layer is impulse heat sealed.

The next layer of protection is a Mylar moisture barrier bag (MBB) which is also impulse heat sealed.

After that we wrap the bag in a visual barrier.

Your box then has all seams sealed and will require a knife to open.

No prying eyes will know what is in your box, and it will disappear into a mail stream of billions of other identical packages.

Please supply your address in the following format:

First Last
123 Main Street
Unit 1
Anytown, ST 12345

Mandatory: Please use specific, compete address. Don't be vague. Please use "123 Main St" or "123 Main Street" and DO NOT use "123 Main".

Mandatory: Please properly abbreviate your state.

Strongly suggested: Use a real name for a real person at that address. Mail addressed to your dog with your maiden name draws suspicion. I can't guarantee delivery to fake or mismatched names.

I DO NOT SHIP TO CALIFORNIA
I DO NOT SHIP INTERNATIONALLY 

All packages have USPS tracking numbers, but I do not provide tracking numbers unless the packages is late or missing.

If you need immediate and constant tracking updates, please sign up for MYUSPS Informed Delivery with the Post Office. It is free, and my shipments will show up automatically.

I only provide tracking on late packages to troubleshoot shipping problems.

If you must request tracking, please include your order number with your request.

In the case that tracking is necessary, it will only be provided encrypted with PGP. Please ensure that your Public Key is uploaded to your profile or included with your message. 

ABSOLUTELY INSANE 125% GUARANTEE

We guarantee delivery.
All packages are tracked.
We require you to properly spell your real name. Packages addressed to your dog will draw attention.
We require properly formatted real addresses.
We offer your choice of 125% re-ship or 100% refund of any order that does not arrive to a proper address provided.

1. In case you are not satisfied with our service please contact us via a private message or email. We are professionals so you can expect us to treat every situation with care and strive to find a mutually agreeable solution.

2. We offer a full reship or a 50% refund in case of seizure or loss of parcel. Also, during holidays postal services are overwhelmed with parcels and staff shortage so there will always be a delay of a few days in delivery time.

7. We might mark the order as shipped even though we might actually send it a day later. This is to prevent LE from trying to identify our delivery pattern.

8. Tracking information is available upon request. It's imporant to remember that we can delay the release of the tracking code if we think it might jeopardize our security protocols or we might not release it at all, only in case of a dispute.

The result was a hybrid with a unique terpene profile that boasts a complex aroma with notes of fuel, skunk, and spice. \nThe genetic backbone of West Coast cannabis varieties, OG Kush arrived in Los Angeles in 1996 when Matt Bubba Berger brought it (along with The Bubba, which was later used to create the famed Bubba Kush) from Florida to legendary cultivator Josh D. Hi White Housers! I am looking for help spreading the word if you like my carts. Please mention me on forums if you enjoy my products. I've beena around for 5 years and I intend to be around for 5 more. 

My listings are new here but I'm not a new vendor and these are well reviewed products. With over 5 years of sales I have booked thousands of 5 star reviews. You can check them out on other top markets or find me on Dred forum. 

Trade Policies:
Here's a general run-down on my trade policies: If you make an order and the product lands at the address given in good tact and makred by the PO then it is considered to be in your posession. Then you must check the merchandise and if it's what you ordered I expect you to close escrow. If you give a bad address or can't find retrieve or obtain posession of your package at the address provided I'm afraid you still must close your escrow and pay for your goods. Repeat customers will possibly recieve a relief offering if the goods were damaged or something odd like that. 

In all other cases if there is some issue such as a leaking cart I will find an equitable solution for you. I will replace the cart and consider time lost. I don't intend to make these errors but my policy is to make all customers feel that they have gotten what was promised or an equitable remedy to any error as we are indeed human and errors are extremely unlikely but possible.

about:
-- Update section --
24-10-19 (Thursday) - all orders will be collected from Thursday and sent on Tuesday 28-10-19 - In future we may stick to sending orders from Tuesday to Thursday, to allow for the extra workload related to all areas of production etc. 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Why choose us?
   Over 30,000 sales since AB and DM, with a solid 99% positive feedback throughout, you can trust us to have integrity and honesty aswell as everything else which makes us better than everyone else. 

   To start, we focus on providing an effective system of care for medicinal patients. That is our mantra and so our prices, especially for the medical kind, are at a reduced price, to make it easier for people to afford this wonderful medicine. 
   We put only the best, most natural and organic ingredients into all of our products. To compliment our extract. 

    We offer everything at a very competitive rate, we compete with ourselves and stick to specific margins, we do not advertise and we pass all savings onto the customer.   We have consistently invested heavily in state of the art equipment in order to bring you the most technically advanced perfect tasting products and formulations. 

    Due to our ongoing investment, experience and existence within the underworld of professional growers we also toll process for large growers and this makes our prices ever more competitive. 

   Without our beloved regular customers we would never have been able to get this far, and so we thank every single one of our customers for sticking with us to the point we are at now. The pinnacle of cannabis.  With mutual respect and faith in eachother we have achieved something great. One love.

!!  It needs explaining how good our techniques are;  For our shatters/waxes and crumbles we use a closed loop system with a dewaxing column and dry ice (-80 celsius), making for a winterized extraction containing virtually no fats, lipids or cellulose which break out of the plant material when extraction is performed at higher temperatures. We use triple distilled butane extra pure gas, which is then purged for 36 - 72 hours at low temperatures under vacuum in our digital vacuum oven, to retain a perfectly purged extract with maximum Terpenes and no hashy overcooked flavours or harsh butane undercookedness. Our aim is to create a dryish honeycomb crumble, a snap and pull, sugar, or Shatter, depending on strain and material quality.

For our RSO, (aclcohol extract), we use isopropyl alcohol, filtration and a rotary evaporator,  which removes plant fibres and heats the alcohol evenly by spinning the flask under vacuum allowing lower temperature, even evaporation and subsequently retains much of the original flavour of the original plant material. Most other People use a rice cooker which over cooks the extract unless very careful. 

We also produce Distillate from our extracts. We have just listed cannabis terpenes. THC and CBD to follow. 

Lastly for our Edible products, experience has shown us the best ways to decarboxylate the THC-a into its active form, THC. We use a digital vacuum oven. This ensures that the high is strong and gets through the blood brain barrier everytime, as opposed to a weak psychoactive body effect which you may have experienced before from other edibles. Our edibles hit strong and come on in waves in controllable sized accurate doses.  We make all our own products from all our own extracts and mostly from our own plants which we grow ourselves. Natural and organic, mostly soil grown. 
      We aim to put the ingredients on all our products which we used to do as standard. (other vendors have since copied our exact ingredients for certain products.

Deliveries will take no longer than 3 days to UK, but on average we get everything delivered in 2-3 days. Bud, vape and wax orders go out NDD usually, edible orders are made in regular batches,
  Latest orders for receiving a weekend delivery is normally Thursday night.

   Have a good time checking out our products.  

   THC Pharmer
       Peace and Love

FAQ (read before messaging please)

How is your BHO extract made?

 Our wax is made from pesticide free plants that we mostly grow ourselves. The buds are cured and dried,  We use a closed loop extractor with a dewaxing column and dry ice to extract at well below freezing temperatures. This produces clearer extracts. 
 We purge the wax  in our vacuum oven under vacuum,  generally until no more bubbles are visible escaping the wax.  As neccesary in some products the fresh THC-a in the wax is decarboxylated into active THC.

When is the cutoff for ordering?

We collect orders everyday by 11am.  The orders are shipped the next day, Monday to Friday and can take up to 5 days to arrive in the UK. (up to 7 days EU), average is 3 to UK

Can you do bulk orders?

for edibles ;

IF it fits through your letterbox, we can send it. the most we can fit is 50 lollies per pack, vacuum sealed.   we generally send up to three items per envelope. SLarge orders can be sent as one if it is possible to vaccuum seal it thin enough. Up to 700 grams.

for vape and bud;

We can fit a lot in an envelope stealthily.

Can i get a custom listing for a bulk order?

Yes, please message first and we will confirm a price. 

can i get tracked shipping?

No, we do not do tracked shipping?

my product has not arrived, what do i do?

We send all packages that have been marked shipped, depending on your previous buying history we will honour a reship. If we feel that you are taking advantage or have no history as a buyer, we will probably not issue a refund or reship in the event of a no show.  In either case it is your decision to raise a dispute and all disputes will be dealt with honesty, dignity and respect. 



How long can i store my edibles?

Gummies can be stored in the freezer for about a month, in the fridge for two weeks.   Lollies last for two months out of the fridge. 
Milk based products can last up to two weeks in the fridge,
Chocolates, last for a month in the fridge. 
   Vape needs to be kept out of the sun and at room temperature. 

My product is not as described, it is unuseable, it has past its sell by date, 

If there is a problem with your product, then please raise a dispute.   This is as useful for us as it is for you because it allows us to identify any errors in the manufacture process. 

Has my package been sent?

We say 2 day delivery,  sometimes it can be a day or two less or more. In general when we mark the product as sent then we have shipped the item that day, so you can estimate, it to arrive the next day or two after marked shipped (or 5 days to EU).
   We cannot answer messages asking when the product will arrive or if it has been shipped, Dream market provides the information you require. 

How many do i take to get high?

As a guide we make every single item to contain 50mg, which we consider a standard dose when consuming cannabis.  We also make microdosed products, which you can enjoy to the same level, but many find that even 10mg of THC is enough for them. 
   Vaping;  when vaping the effective dose is in the 10 mg level, compared to smoking which would be about 50-100mg,  the reason is because smoking wastes a lot of the material. Vaping conserves all the material and is absorbed effectively and quickly, straight to the brain through the bloodstream from inhalation.

What are the ingredients?

the listing should provide the ingredients and hopefully the nutritional information. 

Will I get a free gift?

If bitcoin jumps up during the processing of your order, we normally get a bit excited and add extras.  If you have a unique and interesting username we may add extras,  if you order only bud and we feel that a lolly will help disguise the package we will add some candy. If you have a large order history we will add random things as testers. 

Can I shill for you?

No.

Can I receive a tester for a review?

If you have previous honest reviews, then yes, we are happy to work with you.  . 

Does your vape juice contain synthetic terpenes, nicotine or spice?

Absolutely not, we pride ourselves on producing an almost completely natural product and disagree with selling nicotine or synthetic chemicals. Our vape juices contain vegetable glycerin and propylene glycol. Both approved for consumption over the last 40 years.

What tech shoul dI use to vape?

We reccomend in this order Vaporesso, smok and innokin batteries and a GUARDIAN PRO CCELL TANK.  The wattage should start low about 5 watts and go higher to no more than twenty to fourty watts.  If you burn out a bit you can always go back, the coil will refresh. 
  The same info is true for our Ccell carridges we have for sale.

Can you delete my data?

Yes, We delete data every two weeks, no identifiable information is held by us past that time.
                

---------------


                    we can reship and refund for regular buyers. 

We do not send packages signed or tracked.

about:
THE THC DOCTORS STORE POLICY
Welcome one and all to the THC Doctors HQ.
Here you will find an array of products catering to all your THC vaping needs along with a list of Edibles as well as Shatter and Live Resin, and a list of Terpenes sourced directly from the U.S.A. to allow you to manufacture your own products, a one stop shop for all your THC desires.
WHAT IS THC DISTILLATE?
A drop of distillate sits perched on the edge of a dabbing tool. Taut like a raindrop, this viscus and opaque orb glimmers as it rests within the concave folds of titanium. Encased within this golden drop of goodness is a semi-translucent, 99% pure decarboxylated and distilled tetrahydrocannabinol (THC) sap. Dollar for dollar, this morsel of oil is worth more by weight than just about any other consumable substance on the market, and for good reason: Cannabis oil distillates are arguably the future of cannabis concentrates.
With unmatched purity and sheer versatility, distillate oils provide a clean and potent product with limitless application potential, as well as their potential in offering solutions in various niche markets within the burgeoning cannabis concentrate industry.
We update our products regularly especially with new strains and flavours of Shatter and Resin so please keep checking back for new products and updates.
If you do not see listing quantity that you require please message us, bulk buy orders and custom orders can be arranged
We try our very best to be on here daily, to assist and answer your questions. One of the team will always aim to answer any quandaries that you may have in the same working day, that being said customer service operates during office hours. Please read our terms and policy before asking questions, many will already be answered on there for you.
PLEASE CHECK OUR VENDORS RULES BELOW TO SEE ABOUT OUR SHIPPING TIMES, ESTIMATED DELIVERIES, REFUND POLICIES AND DESTINATIONS.
TOP QUALITY PRODUCTS
All of our pictures are the real product you are getting. We work very closely with growers and distributors in California, who source from organic craft size growers that have been growing in America with decades of experience. The THC Doctor is the connoisseurs alternative, sourcing our medicine from experienced Mom and Pop growers who care, the ones you can trust when it comes to your medicine!
All our distillate that we use for our products is some of the best that we have ever come across, it is triple distilled for purity, smoothness and colour.
Our Shatter and Resins are all *AAA and some of the best that we have found on the market.
We have to say they are about the strongest cannabis product we think we have ever sold.
They have amazing terpene quality and hit like an Iron Mike Tyson left hook, circa early 1980s!!!!
True top draw cannabis products made using Co2 extraction from a top Canadian lab. These are all 100% pesticide free.
All our edibles are made in house by our skilled confectioners and master chocolatiers!
ABOUT OUR OILS
We source our RAW product from a licensed lab in California, who work closely with independent, artisan growers.
We add NO MCT oil or pesticides or any other substances to our THC apart from 12% plant derived organic terpenes (which we also sell on the site). This is a natural plant based substance that will give each THC cart its flavor and smell
(Please find more really interesting and nerdy info about our Terpenes in the section below!)
So that is a 88% THC to 12% Organic Terpense mix, that is it!!
Our carts are 100% SAFE!
** For all our 0.5g and 1g carts we import the RAW product from a distillery in California, we import the best Delta 9 THC Distillate that we have had the pleasure to come across, but we package in the U.K. to avoid importing large containers full of pre-packaged product, as well as shipping costs and imports duties.
The Delta 9 Distillate that we are fortunate enough to have access to is the best of the best and pesticide free. Please check out our ratings and feedback across the markets.
ABOUT OUR TERPENES
Terpenes are the naturally occurring chemicals that give plants their flavors and fragrance. They are what make an apple taste like an apple and make a pine tree smell like pine. A world without terpenes would be extremely bland and boring!
Here at THC HQ we supply specially designed terpenes straight from California and made from pure, natural plant extracts. They are designed to add flavor and interest to your base cannabis strain without changing its specific profile. With our Pure flavor blends, you can revel in countless taste sensations as part of your daily vaping routine.
By adding them to a base cannabis concentrate, you can experience the effects of a totally different strain. A terpenes liquid can change the amount of THC that is admitted into the brain intensifying your high.
Mix with our 1ml 97% Distillate preloaded syringes to create a whole world of flavours!
All our terpenes are:
All Plant Derived, No Glycol, No PEG, No Glycerin.
Because terpenes are so strong, you only need a little bit to liquefy your concentrate or extract and enjoy its effects. To create a vaping solution with terpenes, you only need to use 0.1 ml 0.6 ml of terp juice for each 1 gram of concentrate or extract.
SHOPPING EXPERIENCE
Please check through our Vendor page for all listings, products and our outstanding reviews.
We greatly appreciate the glowing feedback and stellar reviews. If you do think that you have had a pleasant shopping experience with the Doc then please let the rest of world know about. Early auto finalisation on any outstanding orders is always greatly appreciated!
Thank you for shopping with The THC Doctor and we hope to see you all again, soon. Until then stay safe and take care.
No Signature
