WELCOME TO THE RED WHITE  BLUE born in the USA PURE FIRE MDMA source! We do not have customers. We have fans!

NO DUTCH DIRT. Craft synthesized with pride our MDMA is snow white not discolored like DIRTY IMPORTS filled with mercury salts and other NASTY contaminates.

We believe harm reduction is the best path. Harm reduction starts with properly identified safe substances. We present our product as the safest available because we wash it thoroughly to remove contaminants left over from synthesis. Your body will know the difference during your roll and the morning after. We view every single body and mind not harmed by mercury salts and other contaminates a victory. 

Place your order and prepare yourself for the smoothest cleanest MDMA experience you have ever had.

SHIPPING
We currently ship once a week. USPS Priority Mail shipping with top end stealth and tracking  a $10.00 value -- is included on all domestic shipments. USPS Priority Mail time in transit is normally 2 - 4 days.

When sending your address please be sure to encrypt your messages using our PGP key listed on our vendor profile page. Double encrypted is a great way to increase your security and ours if you are up to it.

Please provide address with zip + 4 as shown for enhanced security.

 Address Format
John or Jane Doe
Number Street
City State Zip Code + 4

Please Note: USPS is not 100% reliable so WE DO NOT RESPOND Where is it at? queries until 10 DAYS AFTER marked shipped!

SNOW AW  ARC: The Difference

Snow is our standard product. AW and ARC are product that has been further efined with well-known purification methods.

Acetone wash gets the product white and removes nearly all the odor. But there can still be invisible contaminates and/or solid contaminates.

Re-crystallization places the MDMA back into solution of warm anhydrous isopropyl alcohol. The MDMA solution is then vacuum filtered to remove any non-soluble contaminates. Chilling the filtered solution forces the dissolved MDMA to recrystallize and fall out of solution. Soluble contaminates the acetone may not have completely removed are left in the solute (the liquid part) which is poured off the new crystals and discarded. The new crystals are then vacuum filtered and dried. This results in it being the purest product possible.

What does 84% MDMA Mean?

Before you can make an informed decision about 84% MDMA you first must understand what the number means. Roughly 16% of MDMA hydrochloride -- the salt form with which you are familiar -- is the bonded hydrochloride salt which makes it water soluble the remaining 84% or thereabout being the MDMA base an oil.

So to say it is 84% MDMA base with 16% bonded hydrochloride which makes it into the water-soluble salt we can ingest for the effects is to say it is nearly PURE MDMA hydrochloride. In the case of the typical super lab product this is only true if you accept the leftover byproducts from the synthesis reaction as MDMA. 

We do not. We have found about 15% of the super-lab product is mercury chloride and unfiltered solids -- giving it the tan color. Removing these by products is best accomplished by repeated washing of the MDMA oil base BEFORE CRYSTALLIZATION. Best results require washing until the distilled water (DH2O) used for the wash separates from the MDMA oil base solution and is still clean  crystal clear.

Is this pure? No humans lack technology to create truly pure forms of any substance but it is very high purity. And definitely superior to super-lab products. Our MDMA is produced craft style in small batches at the highest possible quality. After all its first and foremost for ourselves.

SHIPPING AND PROCESSING
- Processing -

May take up to 48 hours to process your order 72 hours in extreme cases.

Processing may be longer for large custom orders in excess of $500. We will notify you in such cases.

- Overnight -

$50 per package.
Not true overnight may arrive within 2-4 days we average about 1.5 days click to door. 

- Combined Shipping -

Shipping must be paid at least once per order sequence. Every item that goes in the same box is eligible for combined shipping after the shipping post has been paid. Rinse and repeat for new order sequences.

- Where do you ship to? -

We ship to 49 out of 50 US states all US territories any college any PO box any reshipping service. We do not ship to California. 

We do not ship internationally. We do not ship to APOs. We do not ship to military bases. 

- Has my order been shipped? -

Your order is shipped as soon as we mark your order as 'shipped' which indicates the label is on the package and is in route to be dropped off where it will be handled by USPS before the cutoff that day. 

We do not guarantee the package will be scanned in on time. Although we will make every effort to do so we do not guarantee that the package will be dropped prior to the cutoff time. 

- Where is my package? -

We kindly ask that you first inquire about your package's location after the first 4 business days Monday through Friday to reduce inquiries. We will provide the expected delivery date. 

- Can I have the tracking number? -

Tracking number information is available in extreme cases or after 7 business days.

- How do I use the 'combined shipping' option? -

You must pay for your first order plus shipping first and then any additional items purchased afterwards will be eligible for the combined shipping option.

- What is the cut off time to get packages shipped the same day as I order? -

11:59 AM est any orders after that time will go out the next business day. I do not work weekends.

- Tracking shows my order as delivered' 'undeliverable' or 'returned to sender.' Can I get a reship or a refund? -

Unfortunately we do not offer recompense for any of these reasons. The only time we offer reship/refund based on shipping is for an item where the tracking has not updated. Ultimately contact me. We are more flexible for VIP members and for users who have been on CGMC for awhile.


FAQ
- Why has my order not been accepted yet? -

Most likely that it was on a weekend. I do not work weekends.

- Why haven't you answered my PM yet? -

Probably since its the weekend and I don't work weekends. 

- Why was my order cancelled/rejected? -

If you are an international customer did not have an address for the order did not pay for shipping sent us your address unencrypted no delivery name or ordering from California. In the even that it is none of these get in touch. 

- I have a shipping question. Where do I look first? -

Please check the Shipping  Processing section on the lefthand sidebar for more information.

- I have a question about my order! What do I do? -

First contact me. Then provide your order ID to me. You will receive an answer without delay. If you do not provide an order ID to me resolving your message inquiry may be delayed by 24-48 hours. 

Please place your order ID in the subject line. Example: 'Order #XXXXXXXXXX' should be the only thing in your subject line. This will automatically link me to your order. 

- Can I have '5000 Bears 5000 Brownies and 400 Hearts'? Custom Listing? -

Yes just ask for a custom listing with what you're wanting so that a custom listing can be created for you specifically.

- What is this white powder on my gummies? Is it okay to consume it? -

The white powder is corn starch which is included to prevent your gummies from becoming a melted glob while in transit. You can consume the corn starch but it might not be very tasty to some. However you can simply rinse the off the gummies in a strainer under ice cold water for a second or two for the best results. Pat dry.

- How can I preserve my gummies? -

Refrigerate them.

- I'm new to edibles how many gummies should I eat to get 'high'? -

The recommended dose is 20mg which is 4 gummies but everyone's body reacts differently so see how it sets with you and slowly work your way up.

- Can I get some compensation for a melted shipment? -

If it's May through August no. Any other time message me.

- My order was returned to sender (RTS). What can I do? -

I do not offer any compensation for an RTS'ed package. This places a great deal of risk upon myself and my OPSEC.

- I got my package but something went wrong! or I got a love letter! -

Contact me.

- I want to leave negative feedback! -

Contact me! Its unfair if you leave that kind of feedback without contacting me prior. 

- Why haven't you communicated with me yet? -

I do not work weekends. Also reach out once every 24 hours if you havent heard from me. 

- I have an issue with an order but it involves my high-end weed. What do I do?

Contact us but we are stringent.

about:
Hello and welcome to our shop. We are the Urban Shamans. We are a small group of people and consider ourselves as city-dwelling healers who, instead of practising on the fringes of society, are hell-bent on balancing the energy levels of the citys adrenally fatigued and negged-out inhabitants. We do this by offering you the best and cleanest spiritual narcotics that we have to offer, and assisting in their usage.

Alas, the ego has expropriated the eco. It has raped, ravaged, and ransacked the beautiful biosphere. Due to nature deprivation, the human spirit has become autistic or dissociative in its relationship with the natural world. Like an autistic child, the human animal has become blind to its psychophysiological interdependence with Mother Earth. This disassociation arises from the confusing split between spirit and flesh.

As urban shamans, we are painstakingly trying to mend this split. We are laying the sustainable groundwork toward a healthier way of being human in accord with Mother Earth. We teach how to rip the ego away from codependence into independence, and then how to rip the ego from independence into an interdependence with all things.

What do certain narcotics do to the human mind?
The honest answer: nobody quite understands. Were really just at the beginning of exploring that frontier. But these substances appear to diminish activity in one very important brain network called the default mode network. That network is very involved with operations having to do with our sense of self: how we integrate whats happening to us in any given moment, with our abiding sense of who we are.

The interesting thing about these substances is that they take this network offline. When that happens, you have this sensation of ego-dissolution: that your self is evaporating or dissolving. And that seems to lead to new connections in the brain temporarily forming. Your emotion center starts talking directly to your visual cortex, lets say, and you see things that youre hoping or fearing. New connections are made that could produce new insights, new perspectives, new ways of looking at the world. And with that you can create a new path for yourself and thus make a positive change.

2.4: Le numero de suivi sera vous sera communiquer au maximum 24h apres l'expedition.

2.5: Merci de FINALISER la vente IMMeDIATEMENT a ReCEPTION du colis. En cas de non respect recurrent de cette regle votre adresse postale pourrait etre bannit de nos services.


3- Feedbacks

3.1: Les feedback sont tres importants pour nous. Si vous netes pas satisfait par une commande  avant de laisser un avis negatif contactez-nousnous essayerons toujours de trouver une solution pour vous dedommager.


4- Remboursements

4.2: Si vous n'avez pas recu votre commande au bout de 21 jours (France) ou 30 jours (EU) a compte de la date d'expedition et que votre numero de suivi n'est pas actif votre commande sera au choix remboursee integralement ou re-expediee.

4.3: Aucun autre motif de remboursement ne sera accepte.


Foire Aux Questions


Q: Comment passer commande ?

R: Vous devez creer une commande pour le produit desire et la quantite voulue ainsi que mettre votre adresse postale. Allez ensuite sur la page de la commande puis envoyez le reglement sur l'adresse de paiement qui est assignee a la commande. Votre commande sera confirmee dans les minutes/heures qui suivent.

Q: Ma commande est marquee comme expediee ou consulter le No. de suivi ?

R: Une fois votre commande expediee le No. de suivi vous sera communiquer par MP sous 24h00. Vous pouvez utliser 17track.net pour suivre l'envoi.

Q: Mon numero de suivi n'est toujours pas actif alors que ma commande a ete expediee

R: C'est tout a fait normal certain suivis s'activent le jour de l'expedition d'autres en court de route et certain a la livraison seulement voire un peu apres. Generalement l'activation du suivi se fait dans les 48h mais ca peut etre plus. Cela est certainement d a l'automatisation (lettre pliee a l'envers ...) et qui ne sont pas correctement scannees par les machines.

about:
**This listing is for 300g tabs of our self-laid 99.93% pure LSD - "Tears of Joy" laid on the Purple Buddha print**

Our LSD is purified at both stages of synthesis (salt, crystal), yielding an exceptionally pure product.

About LSD

Discovered by Dr. Albert Hofmann in 1938, LSD is one of the most potent mind-altering chemicals known. A white, odorless powder usually taken orally, its effects are highly variable and begin within one hour and generally last 8-12 hours, gradually tapering off. It has been used experimentally in the treatment of alcoholics and psychiatric patients. Where it showed some success. It significantly alters perception, mood, and psychological processes, and can impair motor coordination and skills. During the 1950s and early 1960s, LSD experimentation was legally conducted by psychiatrists and others in the health and mental health professions. Sometimes dramatic, unpleasant psychological reactions occur, including panic, great confusion, and anxiety. Strongly affected by SET and SETTING.

If you have never used LSD before:

Use of psychedelics can produce both pleasant and unpleasant experiences. The pleasant experiences can include laughter, insight, beautiful visual effects, spiritual experiences and feeling close to the others who are with you. The unpleasant experiences can include anxiety, panic and fear of losing control. At higher dosages you can believe that death is about to occur. Judgment and coordination can be impaired and injury or trauma can result from acting on bad decisions.

Psychedelics are not addictive or harmful to the body. Multi-day use is not possible as tolerance builds quickly and these drugs will have a limited effect for a few days after use. There are no physical withdrawal effects other than feeling tired the next day.

Dosage - what to expect:

50 micrograms: You can walk in public and interact with friendly people 
100 micrograms: No contact with straight folks for 8 hours 
200 micrograms: You need a safe, predictable environment where you can lie down and listen to relaxing music without interruption 
300 micrograms: You need a safe uninterrupted place to lie down with soft music and a good friend to sit with you for 10 hours. Skill with mediation techniques helps to let go and not fight the experience.

about:
Updates 2020

- Empire Market customers / refugees: THANK YOU for following me over here. 
- If you're curious, I've been vending here for some time now. Things have always went well, but there is a significant trade off of convenience for security. 
- My quick replies that you may be used to from previous markets will likely take a hit due to a more complicated messaging system. 

Late August

March 4 2020

- If your PGP key does not match your market username, I cannot reply to your message. 

April 19 2020

- WHM is probably the most secure market that I've operated on but it is NOT friendly to answer messages on WHM.  If I want to contact the buyer to answer a simple questions I have to import their PGP key to my expansive keychain.  The worst thing about this is that roughly 5% of buyers have a PGP certificate name that matches their market name.  I can't find you on my keychain and don't want to find you unless you have an order with me. 
- That being said WHM is still a great market to vend on.  Most everyone puts in an order without asking questions and kicks back until their pack arrives.  A very few amount of buyers eat up the vast majority of messages.  This is much easier to handle within a different messaging system. 
======

- Thanks WHM Staff for letting me vend here. I will start with a small menu and expand it slowly. 

- I am not a member of Tribe Suess but have been very lucky to have been in great standing 
with DR_SUESS.  I have a healthy stock of fresh DS 3.0 150ug and 200ug Blotters that 
are already printed and laid on cool artwork but I now only have a small reserve of 
raw DS 3.0 for the right custom jobs.  DS_SUESS will take care of his core team first 
before opening up more DS 3.0 Raw Crystal sales to me as I really enjoy doing custom 
layjobs with his crystal. 

============================

Updates 2019

- NO MORE shipping to India. India used to be a major market that was EASY to ship 
to but the population has let corruption take over their mail systems instead of 
resisting bribes and kleptocracy.  Please scroll down for more information. 

- I am now shipping 2C-B HCl blotters at 22mg. Yes blotters at 22mg. Please see my listing for more details and how I made that experience a reality. 

- I am Instrument. I have been everywhere. I have filled over 50000 orders and am excited to start vending on WHM.

- I will no longer send to courier services that forward packs to different countries. I'm able to identify these services and cancel these orders. If you want international mail please pick International shipping.

========= START PROFILE ======

Use the real name of a CURRENT RESIDENT at the address. I NEED a name.

- ALWAYS manually encrypt sensitive information to me.

Do not send packs to an abandoned foreclosed home or house that is for sale. It's very easy to figure these drops out and I will refuse to sort out a solution with you if your pack doesn't land to one of these locations!

Having drugs shipped to a fake name or to a former resident will sometimes be an easy way to land yourself into a law enforcement investigation. Also if you do not provide a name at all I will cancel your order.
====================

My First Class mail packages look extremely boring. People are throwing them in the trash by accident too often. The people most guilty of doing this tend to be wives girlfriends and roommates because they think the business letters are some sort of junky solicitation.

DO NOT THROW THEM AWAY! If someone in your home helps sort out what is or what is not important mail be prepared to pull uninteresting packs from the trash bin and look through them!
================
I am Instrument. I've been around.... I will take your privacy  security very seriously and ship using the most secure and boring methods.

Product

You will receive only premium quality substances. I have zero interest in cutting my gear. Collectively the online drug buying community is exceedingly smart Sending out weak gear is a terrible business model.

Please do research on the drug you are interested in buying before purchasing. Many of the messages that I answer are people asking how much should I take?. I will  answer these questions but the responsible buyer should have already done his/her research.


Shipping

All packs will ship via USPS. Stealth shipping methods will always be used. Please note that your pack will be made to draw zero attention when entering the USPS system and will be Postal Inspector proof. I'm not interested in altering packages to make them mom proof. Your pack will safely get to the address provided. The buyer is responsible for providing an address that is safe from snooping roommates.

All orders will come with at least a Mylar Moisture Barrier bag vacuum seal. .

I use professional labeling and change shipping methods regularly

A note about Express shipping

I do not offer this anymore unless you are willing to pay an extremely steep fee of $135.

Communication

I will answer all messages ASAP. ALWAYS encrypt sensitive information like addresses and names.

I sometimes will reply to your questions in clear text if the context is completely not-sensitive.

PLEASE name your certificate/key the same as your market username.

Payment

Only Monero is accepted. Please finalize when you get your order. If you need to wait several days to test out the product that's okay but please don't forget about me. 

Early finalization is NOT required but always very appreciated and noted. In general I go out of my way to take care of my established customer base.

Sensitive Information

I kill all sensitive information as soon as I'm done with it. I have nothing to benefit from storing your personal information.

F.A.Q.

How long will it take for my pack to land?

An order shipped First Class on Monday will usually land to a metro area on Thursday. 90%+ packs sent on Monday via First Class will land by Saturday. Please hold off on messaging me until your pack has not landed for a full 7 days.

Can you please tell me about international mail?

I do ship LSD to other countries. Packs take anywhere from 6 to 32 days to land. International mail is NOT tracked so I do NOT offer refunds with international mail. All international mail should not require a signature. Your international mail pack will arrive as a very boring letter that the postman will probably just leave in your mailbox.

I do NOT ship to India anymore unless you are already an established customer of mine.  India has become more and more corrupt and inefficient over the years.  Buyers are getting bribed by postmen / government officials to receive their packages and neighborhood kids steal packages. Unless you have a prominent mailing address (E.G. Established and confirmed Medical Facility in South India) I will cancel your order. I'm sorry for this but India has been getting worse every year. 

Average delivery time to Western Europe / Northern Europe / Australia is 9-16 days
Average delivery time to East Asia Korea and Japan is 11-18 days.
Average delivery time to South Asia and the Middle east is 12-22 days.

Can I have my tracking number?

Unless you selected Priority Mail or Express Mail your pack does not come with tracking.

How do refunds work?

If I am provided with a legitimate address then worry not - your pack WILL land. All issues will be handled on a case by case basis. That's my policy.

no more than 5 grams of cannabis (marijuana or hash);

Drug policy of Canada
'On October 17th 2018 cannabis became legal in Canada. The purpose of the Cannabis Act is to protect public health, public safety, and to "[...] create a strict legal framework to control the production, distribution, sale, and possession of cannabis across Canada". The Cannabis Act aims to accomplish 3 goals; keep cannabis out of the hands of youth, keep profits out of the pockets of criminals, and protect public health and safety by allowing adults access to legal cannabis. Individuals who are 18 years of age or older can, "[...] possess, in a public place, cannabis of one or more classes of cannabis the total amount of which, as determined in accordance with Schedule 3, is equivalent to more than 30 g of dried cannabis."

Decriminalization of non-medical cannabis in the United States
In the US the non-medical use of cannabis is decriminalized in 15 states and legalized in another 11 states as of June 2019. Decriminialization refers to a policy of reduced penalties for cannabis offenses, typically involving a civil penalty for possession of small amounts (similar to how a minor traffic violation is treated), instead of criminal prosecution or the threat of arrest. In jurisdictions without any penalties the policy is referred to as legalization, although the term decriminalization is sometimes broadly used for this purpose as well.

'Cannabis in California is legal for both medical and recreational use. In recent decades, the state has been at the forefront of efforts to reform cannabis laws, beginning in 1972 with the nation's first ballot initiative attempting to legalize cannabis. Although Proposition 19 was unsuccessful, California would later become the first state to legalize medical cannabis with the passage of the Compassionate Use Act of 1996 (Proposition 215). In November 2016, California voters approved the Adult Use of Marijuana Act (Proposition 64) to legalize the recreational use of cannabis. 
The legalization of recreational use included statutory authority for local jurisdictions (cities and counties) to regulate or prohibit commercial activities within their jurisdiction. Deliveries cannot be prohibited by local jurisdictions as of January 2019 per BCC Regulation 5416.'  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cannabis_in_California

Growing Marijuana In California
Heres what you should know:
1. The minimum age is 21
2. Possess no more than 6 plants at a time
3. Grow only where you live, where it cannot be seen and lock it
4. Carry no more than 28.5 grams, leave the rest at home
5. Cities can prohibit outdoor growing, but not indoor growing
6. If youre in trouble with the law, get a cannabis lawyer

What is Kratom?

Mitragyna Speciosa  largely referred to as Kratom in English-speaking communities  is a tree grown primarily in Southeast Asia. It may be also known as biak-biak ketum kakuam kraton ithang or thom in these indigenous regions.

It is in the coffee family (Rubiaceae) of flowering plants. Reports of medicinal kratom use in Southeast Asia go back as far as 1836. Some of its traditional applications include treating infection muscle pain and the suppression of coughing and diarrhea.

Kratom generally comes in a powdered form. The leaves of the Mitragyna Speciosa trees are harvested dried and ground before being distributed and sold. Kratom extracts are also available. The most popular methods of ingestion include toss-and-washing (swallowing the powder with water) brewing the powder as a tea or simply chewing the leaves.

Kratom contains over 25 alkaloids which are largely responsible for its psychoactive effects. Two of these alkaloids  mitragynine and 7-hydroxyminitragynine  are thought to be agonists of the -opioid receptor. Activation of this receptor commonly results in sensations of pain relief sedation and euphoria. In animal studies 7-HMG has been found to be nearly 13 times more potent than morphine.

When kratom is ingested the outcome of effects may depend on factors such as the quantity quality strain and user. In general at lower dosages the effect is thought to be more stimulating than sedating. At higher doses the effects are thought to be more sedating than stimulating.

Kratom has garnered significant attention from those attempting to wean themselves off of opiates/opioids (or other drugs) because of its opioid-like behavior. In the past medical researchers have concluded that the therapeutic potential of Kratom  deserves further study. 

It has a sizeable and diverse user base worldwide with many using it to treat anxiety depression pain and fatigue.

Despite its efficacy and potential medical utility kratom is widely misunderstood and under-researched. It remains illegal in many countries. 

The usage of kratom is certainly not risk-free. Adverse long-term effects have been identified and include anorexia weight loss hyperpigmentation psychosis constipation insomnia fatigue and poor concentration.

However in the US all fifteen documented cases of death deemed kratom-related by the DEA were uncited and lacked transparent peer review. In the case of nine kratom-related deaths in Sweden the presence of the kratom-borne alkaloid mitragynine was confirmed alongside O-desmethyltramadol (the active metabolite of tramadol) in autopsy reports . 

At this time no evidence suggests that kratom is definitively toxic or lethal to the human body when used in moderation. More research is required to understand both the long-term and short-term risks of use. The medical literature is clear  there are risks its just question of understanding them better.

about:
Hello all! We're new to Apollon Market, but have been vendors on other marketplaces for the past couple years. We first started vending on Dream where we had 840 sales and a perfect 5 star rating. Unfortunately our stats from Dream are no longer accessible to import over to Apollon, but luckily our stats from Nightmare, Berlusconi, and Cryptonia where we have been vendors on were able to be imported over. As you can see from our nearly flawless ratings from the other marketplaces, we make sure that we deliver exactly what our customers order and try to ship orders out within 24hours of receiving an order, if not ship them out the same day orders are placed. We also only sell GENUINE pharmaceutical meds. We will never give you fakes/presses.
BTW, our listings are all FE only. Don't message us asking to make an escrow listing for you. If you don't want to trust us by placing an order that is FE, then we aren't the right vendor for you. Our ratings speak for themselves on what level of customer service to expect from us. We'll leave it up to you to give us a try. Cheers!
-PSP

---------READ HERE BEFORE ORDERING----------

-If your buyer rating is anything other than 5 stars or have no established purchase history, your order will be rejected on Escrow orders. In lieu of qualifying for this rule, you are welcome to FE when you place your order and you will recieve that order ASAP. I dont ever demand anyone to FE their order, but I can choose who I feel comfortable doing business with. An order that is voluntarily FEd shows me that you are a responsible individual and not a scammer. This rule is also to help financially protect myself due to the amount of careless buyers who do not finalize in a prompt manner.

[Security]

-Encrypt everything that is anyway revealing. Don't be a dummy. ENCRYPT!

[Placing an order]

-READ AND UNDERSTAND THIS: The US mail (usps) is not perfect . We make a promise in our terms of service that we will unconditionally drop your order into the mail system as long as you follow our shipping instructions. What we wont do is promise you that 100% of orders for customers will arrive, but so far we have a very good track record despite occasional delivery delays with usps.

-SIGN UP FOR MYUSPS TO GET TRACKING ON ALL OF YOUR MAIL ! IT IS FREE AND GIVES YOU PEACE OF MIND and will also tell you when they fuck up so you dont think that we are to blame, because we never are.

-We can not and do not offer reships or refunds of any kind if something goes wrong due issues with USPS or if you sent us incorrect shipping info. Any orders that we screw up on, we will work with you on correcting any issues.
Follow the shipping instructions clearly and perfectly and there will not be any problems.
Do not ever order more than you can afford to lose.

-The only people who ever have problems are new customers who dont follow the shipping rules and people who leave bad feedback >>>so they can try and then immediately fail<<< to extort free product from us.

***CRITICAL SHIPPING INSTRUCTIONS: FOLLOW THIS OR YOUR ORDER WILL NOT ARRIVE***

-Send us your exact shipping address that you use to get mail. Send info in all caps if possible. format like this:

CHRISTIE STEVENS
111 SOMEWHERE ST
APT 111
PORN VALLEY, CA 91304-5150

-We will reject anything not formatted like this . this is the formal post office format and will essentially guarantee delivery.

-DO NOT ORDER TO ANYONE BUT YOURSELF!!
there are a few parts to this:
-Do not use a mail forwarding service , people have lost money using these and they are not safe
-Send to college dorms , mail rooms , and hotels at your own risk . anyone filtering your mail might throw this out
-ONLY SEND TO A LOCATION THAT YOU ARE REGISTERED TO GET MAIL AT . this means you filled out that pink card at the post office when you first moved in .
-Do not tell anyone about your order ! theft among friends or room mates is far more common than you might think .
-Do not order to businesses or anywhere you are not the first person to touch the mail. We are not responsible for careless / nosey employees.

-MOST IMPORTANT POINT: ONLY USE A REAL NAME REGISTERED TO YOUR ADDRESS. Do not use initials for any part of your name either. It makes your package look suspicious. If you send us a name using an initial for your first or last name, dont be suprised if the shipping label has your full name printed on it when you receive the order. ;)
-the post will not deliver mail if you are not listed on the address. I dont care if it has worked before, dont do it. ONLY SEND AN ORDER TO A REAL NAME THAT IS REGISTERED TO THAT ADDRESS .
PO Boxes are completely fine.

[Purchase Policies]

-We do not like to cancel or refund orders. Only order when you are absolutely ready for this . We will typically cancel orders due to running out of inventory before being able to update the quantities on our listings

-We do not work inside timeframes. Do not order and tell us to send on a certain date . this is not safe for us . order with the expectation that the item will arrive usually within 1-3 business days with Express or Priority mail options, but on rare occasion up to 5 days or even up to 7 during The holiday season towards the end of the year. Do not order and tell us that you are leaving soon , we may have delays for any number of reasons and we cant work around everyones schedules.

[Shipping Policies]

We want eveyone to be able to try our products with minimum risk . here are our shipping policies:

Our shipping is very fast. We do not ship orders on the weekends. If an order is placed on Fri evening, Sat, or Sun, the order will not be shipped until the next business day. You can count on orders getting shipped out the following business day your order is made. However, we will often attempt to ship the same day we recieve orders and they can be expected to be delivered within:

- 1-2 business days if there is an express mail option
- 2-3 business days in most cases
- 2-15 days maximum

- USA mail is very reliable , but sometimes is slower than expected . please do not message us about a missing order until 10 days from the finalze date have passed . we will make you read this if you do .

- If you ordered something for anyone other than yourself , and had it sent to an address that was not yours , do not waste my time by asking me where the order is . all I can do is tell you if I copied the info down and had it sent . it is against our terms of service to order for anyone other than yourself to your own address .

- Do not ask us for the tracking number ever . It is incredibly annoying . nowhere on this profile or the listing does it say that you get a tracking number even though there will be one. This is for our own safety.

- When you order from us you also are buying: the stamp, the envelope, and the packing materials . this is expensive stuff and doing it this way helps us stay profitable. yay transparency!

-We copy and paste the address you give us directly to the envelope which we make ourselves for each order , using a computer with no internet access .

-Your info is securely destroyed 30 days after the package has been sent . (this is only to reference the order in case there are problems and we can verify that we actually did send it) the only physical copy of your info is the envelope we sent to you and that is it . we use professional grade security measures to keep all info private and secure .

Your safety is our primary concern and you are always very safe with us .

[Customer/vendor purchase agreement]

when you click the purchase button , here is what you are agreeing to :

buyer :
- you agree to read the entire listing and profile before making a purchase , there is very important info that needs to be reviewed so you understand the product .

-You agree that you are a legit buyer and not a scammer trying to leverage feedback or other means against us in any way . very bad idea .

-You agree that I will treat you with the same attitude that you treat me with .

-You agree that your order may be cancelled for any number of reasons , but usually its because we ran out of inventory. Complaining , threatening , or harassing us due to this will get your address saved and your account blacklisted .

vendor :

- I promise to answer any message or question you may have (not answered by this profile) , no matter what. Im a busy girl and some questions are answered by the info above , so i may direct you there .

- I promise to drop your order into the mailbox , and in promising this , I also promise to never lie , cheat , steal or scam . you pay me , you get a package exactly as described . simple as that .

- I promise to ensure complete buyer satisfaction with every transaction to the best of my ability .

-Any threats , hateful speech , or other buffoonery will be promptly mocked and then ignored . we will save and blacklist any address from someone that threatens , harrasses , or tries to steal from us . you dont want to piss off someone who knows where you live .

-Play by the rules . If you violate any of the terms above , there are no reships or refunds . We will do everything in our power to make sure everyone who gives us money is genuinely taken care of.

-Please contact me first before opening any disputed transactions. You can reach me through DM or by email iluvchristiestevens@protonmail.com

Buyers will NOT receive a refund if the tracking indicates the item was unsuccessfully delivered or returned, due to an incorrect address provided to us. FAQ's

1. Question: Can I combine multiple orders into one as to avoid several shipping charges?
Answer : Yes, choose the combined shipping option.

2. Question : Do you grow your offered strains?
Answer: No we do not grow the strains ourselves. 

3. Question : If I order an LB, or more can I mix and match the strains?

6. Question : Can I purchase larger amounts of product that you currently have listed?
Answer : It depends on the product. Please send us a message detailing which product you're interested in and we'll let you know if we have bulk deals available.

7. Question : What is the maximum weight of marijuana you will ship at one time?
Answer : 6 LBS is the max.

8. Question : When will my order be shipped?
Answer : All orders placed before 3:00pm PST will be shipped that same day. Any orders placed after that will be shipped the following day.

9. Question : What if I order Friday or over the weekend.
Answer: Shipping is done daily, Monday  Saturday as orders come in. Full LB units of Marijuana will only ship Monday - Thursday.

10. Question : Do you ship with tracking?
Answer: Yes we ship all orders with tracking. For security reasons we do not provide tracking numbers to any buyers, but we're always happy to check on the shipping status for you at any time.

11. Question : What shipping service do you use and what are shipping times like?
Answer : We ship using USPS Priority Flat Rate. (The Pandemic has impacted delivery ETA'S worldwide, so please be patient.)

12. Question : Can I pay for overnight shipping?
We will only overnight orders for an LB and up. In this situation the buyer will pay for the cost of overnight shipping, as soon as we receive the funds for shipping the product will go out.
